{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"loadstart","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/loadstart_event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>当程序开始加载时，loadstart 事件将被触发。这个事件可以被&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a> 调用，也适用于&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code></a> 和&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a> 元素。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本信息","title":"基本信息","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"规范文档\">规范文档</dt>\n <dd><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/progress-events/\" rel=\" noopener\">Progress</a></dd>\n <dt id=\"接口\">接口</dt>\n <dd>ProgressEvent</dd>\n <dt id=\"冒泡\">冒泡</dt>\n <dd>No</dd>\n <dt id=\"可取消\">可取消</dt>\n <dd>No</dd>\n <dt id=\"目标\">目标</dt>\n <dd>Element</dd>\n <dt id=\"默认动作\">默认动作</dt>\n <dd>None</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Property</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Type</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Description</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>target</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></td>\n   <td>The event target (the topmost target in the DOM tree).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>type</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n   <td>The type of event.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>bubbles</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event normally bubbles or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>cancelable</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event is cancellable or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>lengthComputable </code><span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Specifies whether or not the total size of the transfer is known. Read only.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>loaded</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td>unsigned long (long)</td>\n   <td>The number of bytes transferred since the beginning of the operation. This doesn't include headers and other overhead, but only the content itself. Read only.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>total</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td>unsigned long (long)</td>\n   <td>The total number of bytes of content that will be transferred during the operation. If the total size is unknown, this value is zero. Read only.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://xhr.spec.whatwg.org/#event-xhr-loadstart","title":"XMLHttpRequest Standard"},{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://xhr.spec.whatwg.org/#handler-xhr-onloadstart","title":"XMLHttpRequest Standard"}],"query":"api.XMLHttpRequest.loadstart_event"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关事件","title":"相关事件","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/loadstart_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">loadstart (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/progress_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">progress (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/error_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">error (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/abort_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">abort (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/load_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">load (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/loadend_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">loadend (en-US)</a></code></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/Using_XMLHttpRequest#monitoring_progress\" title=\"/en-US/docs/DOM/XMLHttpRequest/Using_XMLHttpRequest\">Monitoring progress</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"基本信息","id":"基本信息"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"相关事件","id":"相关事件"},{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"当程序开始加载时，loadstart 事件将被触发。这个事件可以被 XMLHttpRequest 调用，也适用于 <img> 和 <video> 元素。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"XMLHttpRequest: loadstart event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"XMLHttpRequest: loadstart イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"loadstart","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/xmlhttprequest/loadstart_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/xmlhttprequest/loadstart_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/comm